'''McColo'''是一家位於美國[[聖荷西_(加利福尼亞州)|聖荷西]]的[[ISP|ISP]]，在2008年下半年因蓄意縱容[[恶意软件|恶意软件]]與[[殭屍網絡|殭屍網絡]]而被其上游[[Global_Crossing|Global Crossing]]與[[Hurricane_Electric|Hurricane Electric]]切斷其連線<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/11/12/AR2008111200658.html|title=Host of Internet Spam Groups Is Cut Off|publisher=華盛頓郵報|date=2008-11-12|accessdate=2010-03-19|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219033417/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/11/12/AR2008111200658.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ithome">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ithome.com.tw/itadm/article.php?c=52018 |title=美ISP切斷最大spammer　全球垃圾信馬上少四成 |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2010-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100312203729/http://www.ithome.com.tw/itadm/article.php?c=52018 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 惡意流量 ==
在2008年11月11日，[[Global_Crossing|Global Crossing]]與[[Hurricane_Electric|Hurricane Electric]]終止McColo的連線之後，[[SpamCop|SpamCop]]觀察到[[垃圾邮件|垃圾邮件]]的總量下滑超過三分之二<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2008/11/12/mccolo_goes_silent/ |title=Net provider accused of coddling crooks yanked offline |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2017-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231001149/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2008/11/12/mccolo_goes_silent/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/securityfix/2008/11/spam_volumes_drop_by_23_after.html |title=Spam Volumes Drop by Two-Thirds After Firm Goes Offline |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109035457/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/securityfix/2008/11/spam_volumes_drop_by_23_after.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在一段時間後，又慢慢恢復到原來的水平<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/03/31/spam-back-to-94-of-all-e-mail/ |title=Spam Back to 94% of All E-Mail |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2011-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111013215157/http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/03/31/spam-back-to-94-of-all-e-mail/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這主要是因為McColo是市場上提供「Bulletproof Hosting」（即使收到反應，[[ISP|ISP]]仍然會讓伺服器維持運作）的主要廠商之一，而本來使用McColo的客戶轉移到其他ISP。

在成功關閉McColo後，許多人將焦點放在其他提供類似服務的[[ISP|ISP]]，如[[Russian_Business_Network|Russian Business Network]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/11/12/AR2008111200658.html |title=Host of Internet Spam Groups Is Cut Off |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2020-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219033417/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/11/12/AR2008111200658.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2008年11月18日時，McColo透過備援線路重新上線，但很快又被終止服務<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://arstechnica.com/security/news/2008/11/mccolo-reconnect-highlights-network-security-gap.ars |title=McColo reconnect highlights network security gap |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2011-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110912052417/http://arstechnica.com/security/news/2008/11/mccolo-reconnect-highlights-network-security-gap.ars |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後公司就關閉了。

在McColo關閉後，受影響最大的是當時全世界最大的殭屍網路[[殭屍網路|殭屍網路]]「[[Srizbi_botnet|Srizbi botnet]]」，在關閉前曾經超過50萬個節點<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2008/11/26/srizbi_returns_from_dead/ |title=Srizbi spam botnet in failed resurrection |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2020-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505230257/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2008/11/26/srizbi_returns_from_dead/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個殭屍網路曾經在一天內發送600億封[[垃圾郵件|垃圾郵件]]，超過當時全世界垃圾郵件量（約1000億封）的一半<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.csoonline.com/article/356219/Srizbi_Grows_Into_World_s_Largest_Botnet |title=Srizbi Grows Into World's Largest Botnet |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2009-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904025943/http://www.csoonline.com/article/356219/Srizbi_Grows_Into_World_s_Largest_Botnet |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

